OL,3,CMan arrested after fire at Jersey
OL,4,Cblock of flats
OL,6,FJersey Police have arrested a 22-year-
OL,7,Fold man in connection with an incident
OL,8,Fat Le Coie Flats in St Helier.
OL,10,FEmergency services say they responded
OL,11,Fto a "small fire" in the building
OL,12,Fopposite Springfield Stadium at 6:30am
OL,13,Fon Monday (22 June) after a report of
OL,14,Fsmoke on the roof.
OL,16,FSeveral roads were closed as
OL,17,Ffirefighters worked to bring the fire,
OL,18,Fmeasuring roughly one metre by one
OL,19,Fmetre, under control.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
