CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1782226088
OL,3,CMan arrested after fire at Jersey
OL,4,Cblock of flats
OL,6,FThere were no reports of injuries and
OL,7,Fno one was evacuated from the area.
OL,9,FAll roads have since reopened and
OL,10,Fpolice say that "business as usual has
OL,11,Freturned to the area".
OL,13,FAn investigation is ongoing, with
OL,14,Fofficers appealing for anyone with
OL,15,Finformation to come forward.
OL,17,FThis includes CCTV or dashcam footage,
OL,18,Falongside any witnesses who may have
OL,19,Fseen the fire being started or someone
OL,20,Facting suspiciously.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/3
